  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nCurrently, to run Snap Sync both options have to be set to TRUE: FastSync and SnapSync\r\nIt's because the Snap Sync is just a subset of FastSync. \r\nUnfortunately it's not intuitive for the users and they tend to set FastSync to False \r\nWe could improve our docs but maybe a better option is to treat SnapSync option as an override and whenever it's set to True treat FastSync as also being set to True.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nModify MultiSyncModeSelector\r\nWe can do it as @LukaszRozmej suggested here:\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/issues/4008\r\n",
